<noinclude>Links to Jira issues and queries via interwiki links.
* Use <code>{{Jira|key=PROJECT-123}}</code> to link to a specific issue (uses the <code>jira</code> interwiki prefix).
* Use <code>{{Jira|jql=...}}</code> to link to a Jira filter by JQL (uses the <code>jira-jql</code> interwiki prefix).
